@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 6
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

' —— 参与者简约配色（低饱和） ——
skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor<<Dev>> #EDF8FF
  BorderColor<<Dev>> #C6E9FF
  FontColor<<Dev>> #10304A

  BackgroundColor<<Dashboard>> #FFF9F0
  BorderColor<<Dashboard>> #F3E8D6
  FontColor<<Dashboard>> #4A3A1A

  BackgroundColor<<Nacos>> #F6FFF6
  BorderColor<<Nacos>> #DFF7E6
  FontColor<<Nacos>> #0F3E2F

  BackgroundColor<<App>> #F7F9FF
  BorderColor<<App>> #E6EEF9
  FontColor<<App>> #18203D
}

participant "开发者" as Dev <<Dev>>
participant "可视化服务" as Dashboard <<Dashboard>>
participant "Nacos 配置中心" as Nacos <<Nacos>>
participant "业务应用A" as AppA <<App>>
participant "业务应用B" as AppB <<App>>

' —— 生命线 & 激活条使用统一低调高亮 ——
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #556575
  LifeLineBorderColor #E6EDF3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActivationBorderColor #9FC8FF
  ActivationBackgroundColor #E8F4FF
}

Dev -> Dashboard: 可视化管理操作
activate Dashboard
Dashboard -> Nacos: 读取 / 更新 配置
activate Nacos

Nacos -> AppA: 推送配置变更
activate AppA
AppA -> AppA: 动态更新线程池
deactivate AppA

Nacos -> AppB: 推送配置变更
activate AppB
AppB -> AppB: 动态更新线程池
deactivate AppB

deactivate Nacos

Dashboard -> AppA: 直接获取运行状态
activate AppA
AppA -> Dashboard: 返回监控数据
deactivate AppA

Dashboard -> AppB: 直接获取运行状态
activate AppB
AppB -> Dashboard: 返回监控数据
deactivate AppB

Dashboard -> Dev: 展示完整监控视图
deactivate Dashboard

note over Dashboard, Nacos
  核心设计理念：
  • 底层数据源依然是配置中心
  • Dashboard 作为轻量可视化代理
  • 业务应用仅依赖配置中心，无需感知 Dashboard
  • 实现了轻量和功能性的平衡
end note

@enduml
